
Fill in .env file in root directory
Fill in contract address in mint-nft.js with contract address after deployment
Replace "image: XXXXXX" with IPFS URI (IPFS or Pinata) in example-metadata.json
Replace mintNft parameter with metadata.json pin URL(IPFS or Pinata) in mint-nft.js

